==English==
===Etymology===
from [[w:Hans Christian Gram|Hans Christian Gram]] Danish bacteriologist
===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|Gram staining}}
'''Gram's method'''
#{{medicine}} a [[staining]] [[technique]], using a sequence of [[crystal violet]], [[iodine]] and [[safranine]], used to [[differentiate]] [[bacteria]] into two large groups of [[species]]
